<bibRefCitation author="Rahman, AKA" journalOrPublisher="Asiatic Society of Bangladesh, Dhaka, Bangladesh" pageId="0" pageNumber="299" refId="B35" refString="Rahman, AKA, Kabir, SMH, Ahmad, M, Ahmed, ATA, Ahmed, ZU, Begum, ZNT, Hassan, MA, Khondoker, M, 2009. Encyclopedia of flora and fauna of Bangladesh, Vol. 24. Marine Fishes. Asiatic Society of Bangladesh, Dhaka, Bangladesh" title="Encyclopedia of flora and fauna of Bangladesh, Vol. 24. Marine Fishes." year="2009">Rahman et al. 2009</bibRefCitation>
